00:15:56.372 --> 00:16:00.626 align:middle line:10%
when you can feel the
feelings create 0.1 Hertz,

00:16:00.626 --> 00:16:02.503 align:middle line:10%
you're harmonizing your
heart and your brain.

00:16:02.503 --> 00:16:06.215 align:middle line:84%
And in addition to everything
else that we've already said,

00:16:06.215 --> 00:16:08.676 align:middle line:84%
in addition to all of the
other benefits of intuition

00:16:08.676 --> 00:16:10.970 align:middle line:84%
and subconscious access
and all of those things,

00:16:10.970 --> 00:16:13.389 align:middle line:84%
super learning, triggering
the immune response,

00:16:13.389 --> 00:16:14.891 align:middle line:84%
triggering your
anti-aging hormones,

00:16:14.891 --> 00:16:16.767 align:middle line:84%
in addition to all
of those things,

00:16:16.767 --> 00:16:19.437 align:middle line:84%
you are creating more
resilience in your life.

00:16:19.437 --> 00:16:22.064 align:middle line:84%
The more you practice this
technique, the greater

00:16:22.064 --> 00:16:24.483 align:middle line:84%
resilience you
have in your life.

00:16:24.483 --> 00:16:27.069 align:middle line:84%
So I'd like to take
this conversation now

00:16:27.069 --> 00:16:30.156 align:middle line:90%
to an even deeper level.

00:16:30.156 --> 00:16:34.952 align:middle line:84%
By going deeper, it's
going to also go global.

00:16:34.952 --> 00:16:39.248 align:middle line:84%
Because what we now know is
that the act of us having

00:16:39.248 --> 00:16:42.835 align:middle line:84%
this experience, this
heart-brain harmony, not only

00:16:42.835 --> 00:16:46.589 align:middle line:84%
does it create coherence
within our bodies,

00:16:46.589 --> 00:16:49.717 align:middle line:84%
it is also the key
to creating coherence

00:16:49.717 --> 00:16:52.011 align:middle line:84%
in the field that
connects all things.

00:16:52.011 --> 00:16:53.804 align:middle line:84%
And as you'll see
in a moment, that

00:16:53.804 --> 00:16:55.389 align:middle line:90%
can be a really good thing.

00:16:55.389 --> 00:16:57.850 align:middle line:90%
Personal coherence is good.

00:16:57.850 --> 00:17:00.061 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about
global coherence,

00:17:00.061 --> 00:17:02.188 align:middle line:90%
and that's really good.

00:17:02.188 --> 00:17:05.900 align:middle line:84%
There is a magnetic field
that surrounds our planet.

00:17:05.900 --> 00:17:09.069 align:middle line:84%
And this magnetic field, the
magnetic field of the Earth, it

00:17:09.069 --> 00:17:11.113 align:middle line:90%
permeates all things.

00:17:11.113 --> 00:17:15.159 align:middle line:84%
Everything is part of this
magnetic field, every blade

00:17:15.159 --> 00:17:18.454 align:middle line:84%
of grass, every hamster,
every goldfish, every CEO

00:17:18.454 --> 00:17:21.874 align:middle line:84%
of every corporation, every
leader of every nation,

00:17:21.874 --> 00:17:24.585 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to the
magnetic fields of the Earth,

00:17:24.585 --> 00:17:28.381 align:middle line:84%
there is no them and
