00:17:28.381 --> 00:17:31.342 align:middle line:84%
And that means we are all
connected by this field.

00:17:31.342 --> 00:17:33.094 align:middle line:84%
And what happens
in this field is

00:17:33.094 --> 00:17:35.054 align:middle line:90%
really important for all of us.

00:17:35.054 --> 00:17:37.306 align:middle line:90%
It's important to you and to me.

00:17:37.306 --> 00:17:39.850 align:middle line:84%
And it's important to the
scientists of the world who

00:17:39.850 --> 00:17:42.395 align:middle line:90%
