00:19:29.168 --> 00:19:33.297 align:middle line:84%
So when the sun goes
through a period of time

00:19:33.297 --> 00:19:36.926 align:middle line:84%
where the sunspot
cycle is high, it

00:19:36.926 --> 00:19:39.845 align:middle line:84%
means there are a lot of
magnetic storms on the sun,

00:19:39.845 --> 00:19:41.555 align:middle line:84%
so it's not
surprising that would

00:19:41.555 --> 00:19:44.683 align:middle line:84%
influence the magnetic
fields of the Earth.

00:19:44.683 --> 00:19:47.561 align:middle line:84%
This is where the
biology comes into it.

00:19:47.561 --> 00:19:51.857 align:middle line:84%
The strongest magnetic field
in your body, the strongest

00:19:51.857 --> 00:19:54.610 align:middle line:84%
biological magnetic field
is not in your brain,

00:19:54.610 --> 00:19:56.153 align:middle line:90%
it's in your heart.

00:19:56.153 --> 00:19:57.488 align:middle line:90%
Your brain has a magnetic field.

00:19:57.488 --> 00:19:59.323 align:middle line:84%
The heart is much,
much stronger.

00:19:59.323 --> 00:20:01.075 align:middle line:90%
So now we're seeing a link.

00:20:01.075 --> 00:20:03.452 align:middle line:84%
Magnetic fields of the sun,
magnetic fields of the Earth,

00:20:03.452 --> 00:20:05.287 align:middle line:90%
magnetic fields of the heart.

00:20:05.287 --> 00:20:07.790 align:middle line:84%
Now you can see why
we would be influenced

00:20:07.790 --> 00:20:10.167 align:middle line:90%
