00:20:10.167 --> 00:20:13.421 align:middle line:84%
So this relationship
is one of the reasons

00:20:13.421 --> 00:20:15.840 align:middle line:84%
that scientists are
interested in tracking

00:20:15.840 --> 00:20:18.050 align:middle line:84%
what it is that's happening
in the magnetic fields

