00:20:27.393 --> 00:20:31.397 align:middle line:84%
comes into play with why what
I'm about to describe to you

00:20:31.397 --> 00:20:34.900 align:middle line:84%
was a mystery originally
to scientists.

00:20:34.900 --> 00:20:37.445 align:middle line:84%
It took a tragedy,
unfortunately,

00:20:37.445 --> 00:20:42.074 align:middle line:84%
for scientists to really wake up
to how deep this connection is

00:20:42.074 --> 00:20:44.577 align:middle line:84%
between us and the magnetic
fields of the Earth,

00:20:44.577 --> 00:20:48.247 align:middle line:84%
between our hearts and the
magnetic fields of the Earth.

00:20:48.247 --> 00:20:51.584 align:middle line:84%
The information that comes
back from these satellites,

00:20:51.584 --> 00:20:54.962 align:middle line:84%
it is charted every
day, two satellites,

00:20:54.962 --> 00:20:58.424 align:middle line:84%
called the geosynchronous
orbital satellites, or GOES,

00:20:58.424 --> 00:21:01.135 align:middle line:90%
G-O-E-S, for short.

00:21:01.135 --> 00:21:04.305 align:middle line:84%
We have GOES number one
and GOES number two.

00:21:04.305 --> 00:21:06.390 align:middle line:84%
What you're seeing
on your screen

00:21:06.390 --> 00:21:11.020 align:middle line:84%
is a chart that shows
these magnetic fields being

00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:14.773 align:middle line:84%
plotted as a result of what
the satellites have sent to us.

00:21:14.773 --> 00:21:17.776 align:middle line:84%
And each box represents
a 24-hour period of time.

00:21:17.776 --> 00:21:20.446 align:middle line:84%
So you can see, every 24 hours,
they ebb, they flow, they ebb

00:21:20.446 --> 00:21:21.238 align:middle line:90%
and they flow.

00:21:21.238 --> 00:21:22.781 align:middle line:90%
Scientists know this.

00:21:22.781 --> 00:21:24.450 align:middle line:10%
One of the satellite's
data is in red,

00:21:24.450 --> 00:21:27.036 align:middle line:10%
the other one is in blue.

00:21:27.036 --> 00:21:30.247 align:middle line:10%
One day, as scientists
were watching this data,

00:21:30.247 --> 00:21:31.832 align:middle line:10%
there was a huge
spike that happened.

00:21:31.832 --> 00:21:34.335 align:middle line:10%
And the scientists are saying,
we've never seen that before,

00:21:34.335 --> 00:21:35.127 align:middle line:10%
what on Earth?

00:21:35.127 --> 00:21:37.880 align:middle line:10%
And what on Earth is happening
to the magnetic fields

00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:39.965 align:middle line:10%
of the Earth to
create this spike?

00:21:39.965 --> 00:21:42.343 align:middle line:10%
So they took the data
and they overlaid it

00:21:42.343 --> 00:21:44.220 align:middle line:10%
onto a calendar of time.

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:47.932 align:middle line:10%
So they could see what
date that spike occurred.

00:21:47.932 --> 00:21:49.475 align:middle line:10%
And it's probably
no surprise to you,

00:21:49.475 --> 00:21:51.727 align:middle line:10%
because I've referenced
this in the past.

00:21:51.727 --> 00:21:53.479 align:middle line:10%
It was a big surprise
to the scientists.

00:21:53.479 --> 00:21:57.816 align:middle line:10%
That spike happened at
9:00 AM Eastern Standard

00:21:57.816 --> 00:22:02.905 align:middle line:10%
Time, September 11,
2001, 15 minutes

00:22:02.905 --> 00:22:05.407 align:middle line:10%
after the first plane hit the
first tower of the World Trade

00:22:05.407 --> 00:22:07.243 align:middle line:10%
Center.

00:22:07.243 --> 00:22:09.870 align:middle line:84%
The reason this is important
is because scientists believe

00:22:09.870 --> 00:22:14.333 align:middle line:84%
it took about 15 minutes for
the images of the tragedy

00:22:14.333 --> 00:22:17.419 align:middle line:84%
to travel through the media,
through the satellites

00:22:17.419 --> 00:22:21.173 align:middle line:84%
and the televisions, all around
the world for people to see,

00:22:21.173 --> 00:22:23.842 align:middle line:84%
and that the magnetic
spike that we

00:22:23.842 --> 00:22:29.139 align:middle line:84%
were seeing from the satellites
measuring Earth's field

00:22:29.139 --> 00:22:33.978 align:middle line:84%
was actually the result of
hundreds of thousands, probably

00:22:33.978 --> 00:22:36.855 align:middle line:84%
millions or even
billions of people

00:22:36.855 --> 00:22:42.111 align:middle line:84%
watching the data in the same
moment in time simultaneously.

00:22:42.111 --> 00:22:44.780 align:middle line:84%
Hundreds of thousands,
millions or billions of people

00:22:44.780 --> 00:22:48.242 align:middle line:84%
are watching the tragedy
through the media,

00:22:48.242 --> 00:22:51.996 align:middle line:84%
and they are having a
heart-based response

00:22:51.996 --> 00:22:54.957 align:middle line:84%
to what they're seeing,
an emotional response.

00:22:54.957 --> 00:22:57.626 align:middle line:84%
Now a lot of different
responses, some were angry,

00:22:57.626 --> 00:22:59.878 align:middle line:84%
some were afraid,
some were saddened.

00:22:59.878 --> 00:23:03.882 align:middle line:84%
The key is they were all
heart-based experiences.

00:23:03.882 --> 00:23:07.052 align:middle line:84%
All of a sudden, from a
purely physics point of view,

00:23:07.052 --> 00:23:09.179 align:middle line:84%
we have hundreds,
possibly millions

00:23:09.179 --> 00:23:12.850 align:middle line:84%
of human magnetic
fields from the heart

00:23:12.850 --> 00:23:16.437 align:middle line:84%
that are now
collectively feeding

00:23:16.437 --> 00:23:20.566 align:middle line:84%
the greater magnetic field of
the Earth, spiking that field.

00:23:20.566 --> 00:23:22.109 align:middle line:84%
Now this is a surprise
to scientists,

00:23:22.109 --> 00:23:23.694 align:middle line:84%
because their
conditioning, as you

00:23:23.694 --> 00:23:27.364 align:middle line:84%
saw earlier in this episode,
or earlier in this series,

00:23:27.364 --> 00:23:30.117 align:middle line:84%
is that we are separate
from the Earth.

00:23:30.117 --> 00:23:31.910 align:middle line:84%
And if we're separate,
there's no way

00:23:31.910 --> 00:23:34.538 align:middle line:84%
that humans could influence the
magnetic field of the planet.

00:23:34.538 --> 00:23:36.582 align:middle line:84%
So scientists weren't
expecting this.

00:23:36.582 --> 00:23:39.627 align:middle line:84%
This was the wake up
call that said, my god,

00:23:39.627 --> 00:23:42.630 align:middle line:84%
look, not only are we
connected, but we're

00:23:42.630 --> 00:23:47.259 align:middle line:84%
so deeply connected that we can
influence the magnetic field

00:23:47.259 --> 00:23:49.345 align:middle line:90%
of an entire planet.

00:23:49.345 --> 00:23:51.013 align:middle line:90%
Here's why that's important.

00:23:51.013 --> 00:23:54.516 align:middle line:84%
If you remember what
happened on the Earth,

00:23:54.516 --> 00:23:57.478 align:middle line:84%
in major population centers
all over the world, at least

00:23:57.478 --> 00:24:00.689 align:middle line:84%
for the first few
days after 9/11,

00:24:00.689 --> 00:24:04.234 align:middle line:84%
there was more cooperation,
there was more harmony.

00:24:04.234 --> 00:24:08.155 align:middle line:84%
We were truly a family, at
least for a couple of days.

00:24:08.155 --> 00:24:11.367 align:middle line:84%
People looked at one another
on the streets of major cities.

00:24:11.367 --> 00:24:12.451 align:middle line:90%
They made eye contact.

00:24:12.451 --> 00:24:14.703 align:middle line:90%
They hugged one another.

00:24:14.703 --> 00:24:17.873 align:middle line:84%
We felt like families, one
of the most peaceful times

00:24:17.873 --> 00:24:19.458 align:middle line:84%
in recent times,
in modern times,

00:24:19.458 --> 00:24:20.626 align:middle line:90%
in the history of the world.

00:24:20.626 --> 00:24:22.294 align:middle line:90%
Why did that happen?

00:24:22.294 --> 00:24:26.590 align:middle line:84%
Scientists attribute
that harmony

00:24:26.590 --> 00:24:29.677 align:middle line:84%
to the spike in the magnetic
fields of the Earth.

00:24:29.677 --> 00:24:31.095 align:middle line:90%
And here's why.

00:24:31.095 --> 00:24:33.806 align:middle line:84%
When the magnetic
fields are strong,

00:24:33.806 --> 00:24:38.102 align:middle line:84%
people are less aggressive,
people are more cooperative,

00:24:38.102 --> 00:24:40.187 align:middle line:84%
they're more willing
to work together

00:24:40.187 --> 00:24:41.188 align:middle line:90%
to solve their problems.

00:24:41.188 --> 00:24:45.484 align:middle line:84%
When the magnetics are weak,
people become more aggressive,

00:24:45.484 --> 00:24:49.571 align:middle line:90%
conflict becomes more available.

00:24:49.571 --> 00:24:51.323 align:middle line:84%
Doesn't mean it has
to happen, but there's

00:24:51.323 --> 00:24:53.492 align:middle line:90%
more of a tendency toward that.

00:24:53.492 --> 00:24:57.079 align:middle line:84%
When those magnetic fields are
low, we are more aggressive.

00:24:57.079 --> 00:24:59.998 align:middle line:84%
So the elevation of
the magnetic fields

00:24:59.998 --> 00:25:05.003 align:middle line:84%
created a temporary aura
of peace upon the Earth.

00:25:05.003 --> 00:25:07.214 align:middle line:84%
And that was the
